{"tid":174868,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李彩華美國抽獎中9000美元","createTime":"2017-03-27T06:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T07:36:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60e5cb855a869815b4871be8ee3fe929a2b6d118","tid":174868,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170210/s00092/68442a3f9924e019059ae1e0fae9cf2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170210%2Fs00092%2F68442a3f9924e019059ae1e0fae9cf2b.jpg&h=a9c18193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】李彩華昨日出席apm情人節活動，她透露農曆新年先和母親往美國旅行兼探同學，接着再跟朋友去韓國滑雪。一向沒抽獎運的她，在拉斯維加斯的抽獎活動中，抽中二獎9000美元；不過，她購物時遇蝦碌事，她拿起蠟燭台時，不慎打爛蓋子，這蠟燭台要數千港元，但售貨員當作損耗，不用她賠償。李彩華又自爆在韓國滑雪撞傷膝蓋：「是內傷，沒表面傷痕，但都要去求診。」<br />\n未想嫁人<br />\n情人節將至，李彩華會在上海工作，男友剛巧也到當地公幹，工作後大家可共度情人佳節。笑言男友現在送什麼給她，也未能帶來驚喜，除非求婚。若真的求婚，她會否答應？李彩華說：「我們有共識，多工作1、2年才結婚，現在科學昌明，遲些生BB也不成問題。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170210/s00016/1486663118740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170210%2Fs00016%2F1486663118740&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=f7f92e4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170210%2Fs00016%2F1486663118740&h=2db0ba4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170210/s00016/1486663118740</a>"},{"pid":"65c41758c4694180c59bcda57803e505ef16615d","tid":174868,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885abb37da878c27f8c29307228c1861bb7b0cfe","tid":174868,"uid":60506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"以為男果個"},{"pid":"413e796c50fa379e757576388234f73e3527ebcc","tid":174868,"uid